{"tid":429948,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"陸續有黎  攞機2日叉電離奇冒煙 強國女果粉搵水淋","createTime":"2017-10-09T11:29:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T14:27:22.000Z","uid":141060,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1068ad172c592826089ddea7eb3da7b76915753a","tid":429948,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:29:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20171009&amp;guid=57310697&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20171009%26guid%3D57310697%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&d=hAoLjnH3VPVtREvRwMsKRNZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=5457a6b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20171009%26guid%3D57310697%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&h=83decf46\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20171009&amp;guid=57310697&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n蘋果iPhone 8系列手機推出不足1月，惟質素事故頻生，繼多名用家反映手機電池膨脹，令外殼爆開後，浙江嘉興今天更有用家發現使用2日的iPhone 8離奇冒煙。<br />\n<br />\n事主小敏在嘉興市區的證券公司上班，手上的64GB銀色iPhone 8是父親買了新股有斬獲後，在國慶期間從安徽馬鞍山老家經銷商買來送她的。<br />\n<br />\n她前日取得手機，昨晚11時許睡覺前，便將手機插上充電器。大約凌晨時份，她醒來，迷迷糊糊去洗手間，其間看到廚房冒煙。她走過去一看，驚見正在充電的iPhone 8燒起來。小敏指「煙很大，有沒有明火沒注意看。」但手機不斷傳出東西燒着的劈啪聲。<br />\n<br />\n小敏當時看到廚房有水，即時將水淋在手機上。不過她強調，自己雖然忘記拔走充電器，但已把插座的開關關掉了。不過淋完水後，煙卻越大越濃，小敏見狀，即跑回了房間，聽不到聲音才出來。今天早上7時許，小敏見iPhone 8已彎曲的，側面被撐開。<br />\n<br />\n小敏取電話卡和拍照後便上班，繼而再跟蘋果官方客戶服務部職員聯絡。雖然已提供相片，另蘋果客服表示工作時間內4個小時會回覆，惟至今仍未收到任何消息。小敏坦言只希望蘋果將其手機修理或安排換新機。<br />\n<br />\n《都市快報》<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/09/192825_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F09%2F192825_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=63ab3cbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/09/192828_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F09%2F192828_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b0787e17&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f26118a00ae3e55d34b39e0d2eb31a7a3315f47","tid":429948,"uid":128600,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:41:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n全球回收<br />\n<br />\n禁iphomr 8上機"},{"pid":"ebf3f4aece75823d6dca2599d50625536c98c41b","tid":429948,"uid":14170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:41:57.000Z","msg":"用水淋都無爆炸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"def8edd2fdb3906723f7d4bf652d3eedb6a78ea7","tid":429948,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:42:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n全球回收<br />\n<br />\n禁iphomr 8上機</blockquote><br />\n下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有爆炸咋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e181829c89e024bec51b8951bd294921489735db","tid":429948,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:46:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"114d3b95377f919c5e29200d611d5751ef56a3cb","tid":429948,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T11:47:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用水淋都唔爆炸<br />\n<br />\n買得過啦</blockquote><br />\nNote8 應該炸死左條白癡妹了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf59236a6ab5bd4666ecb624a01521c3df24cab9","tid":429948,